4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential skills in JavaScript and Python over 18 weeks. The program features 3 classes weekly with a small class size of 1 instructor per 7 students, ensuring personalized attention. No prior coding skills are required, and lessons are available in both English and Spanish.

Participants will learn to build applications, utilize APIs, and complete a final project to gain hands-on experience. Graduates receive a certificate in Full-Stack Development.

For more information, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer. 

